Package dk.anaha.easykv.client

Package with client libraries for EasyKeyValue.
Author:
Azri Rosborg
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EasyKVWatcher
    This interface supports the use of watchers for changes to a key in the key/value store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EasyKVJava
    EasyKVJava is a EasyKeyValue client which method names that resemble pure Java.
    EasyKVR
    EasyKVR is a EasyKeyValue client which method names that resemble Redis.
    EasyKVZK
    EasyKVZK is a EasyKeyValue client which method names that resemble Apache ZooKeeper.
